CollabIRCate is a free, open-source collaboration tool. It leverages 
existing services and environments, IRC, mail, the web, rather than 
trying to force you to learn Yet Another Tool.

Testing the system:

[skaro:~/collabircate] justin% perl Makefile.PL
...
Writing Makefile for CollabIRCate
[skaro:~/collabircate] justin% bin/deploy.pl 
[skaro:~/collabircate] justin% make test
...
All tests successful.
Files=8, Tests=29,  3 wallclock secs ( 0.04 usr  0.03 sys +  2.30 cusr  0.34 csys =  2.71 CPU)
Result: PASS

All good!
